    <h1>Zero-Party Data</h1>
    <p class="description">Information a customer <strong>deliberately and proactively shares</strong> with a brand — preferences, intentions, and personal context. The most accurate, most privacy-compliant data type, and the strategic alternative to third-party cookies in 2026.</p>
